 
<p>
Some Republicans have used <a href="https://www.techdirt.com/2022/07/15/why-the-gop-wants-to-break-your-spam-filter-gop-candidate-tricked-gullible-voters-into-funding-him-with-misleading-spam-emails/">misleading fund-raising emails</a>,
and now Republicans are pressuring businesses to exempt
their fund-raising emails from laws against spam.  They also
want to pass a law that their emails cannot be treated as spam.

 